# Docker build ignore rules for the ECS benchmark image.
#
# The build context for this image is the parent directory that holds both the
# `lightstream` and `minarrow` checkouts (see Dockerfile and run.sh), so these
# patterns are matched against `lightstream/...` and `minarrow/...`. `run.sh`
# and `run-local-docker.sh` stage this file into the context root as
# `.dockerignore` before building and remove it afterwards, because Docker only
# reads `.dockerignore` from the context root.
#
# Everything under the context is excluded except the two checkouts the image
# builds, so whatever else lives beside them stays out of the context. Build
# output and VCS metadata within the checkouts are excluded to keep the
# context small and the build reproducible.

*
!lightstream
!minarrow

**/target/
**/.git/
**/.github/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/.DS_Store
